commit.message:
Fix document building (#186)

Lock to a specific revision of our custom doc plugin, that way we won't
pull a volatile release. The final release of Material isn't too far
away, but we don't want to break between now and then.

commit.message:
Remove unused variable MODULE (#185)

* Remove unused variable MODULE

Removing this line removes the only reference to `__file__`, which
allows tools like pyoxidizer to create standalone binaries that depend
on this package. See also:
https://github.com/indygreg/PyOxidizer/issues/69

* Remove unused os import
